[[Moff/Legends|Moff]] '''Poliff''' was in control of the [[Tunka sector/Legends|Tunka sector]] and had a close relationship with [[Tyanna Tymb]]. Tyanna would give both him and [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Fessix]] information about her [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] clients, even though [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub Corporation]] was on the side of the Republic.

